f leading-edge technologies including the SourceÂ® game engine and SteamÂ®, a leading platform for digital content offering thousands of games to millions of users around the world. In 2015, Valve introduced the Steam Hardware devices, a collection of hardware devices designed to extend Steam beyond the desktop. In 2016, launched SteamVR, a platform for the creation and distribution of leading edge VR products. Today, Valve is composed of over 300 of the industry's best artists, programmers, and writers. In the company's history, it has risen from \"unlikely new entry\"â to industry leader, producing a string of best-selling and critically-acclaimed PC products and technologies."
